   TOKYO, SYDNEY
</DATELINE>
<TEXT>
MATSUSHITA Electric Industrial, a leading manufacturer of electronic goods
in Japan, plans to issue Y200bn (Dollars 1.8bn) of straight corporate bonds
next quarter, the company announced yesterday, AP-DJ reports from Tokyo.
