FT  21 MAY 93 / Construction Contracts: Football stadium
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
EC HARRIS reports that the Pounds 3.1m improvement of Coventry City Football
Club's Highfield Road stadium has started on site. E C Harris is acting as
employer's agent.
The FA Premier League club is bringing its ground up to the standards of the
